  "remarks": "KPe.014. Used as an alias by the Korea Mining Development Trading Corporation (KOMID) to carry out procurement activities. KOMID was designated by the Committee in April 2009 and is the DPRK's primary arms dealer and main exporter of goods and equipment related to ballistic missiles and conventional weapons.; Listing: Listed on 22 January 2013 pursuant to UNSC resolution 2087 (2013)",
